{"tid":227053,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"又話上大學會好舒服唔使讀書","createTime":"2017-05-03T01:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:22:47.000Z","uid":4596,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40ab53ed88122cab3df4bd38bf3b42d96b63095a","tid":227053,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:19:46.000Z","msg":"大佬我真係讀得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五月有六個考試等緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5個係practical<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 首先要背嘅嘢有好多,真係多過成個DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要識apply+practical skills<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒一科都係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊啲人好似個個都識哂咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師點解你要呃我大學好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之留返係香港讀science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:大英帝國醫療科"},{"pid":"86897e63c1477f506c971074e5aae17b632b8b07","tid":227053,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"我都係6個exam 真係喊出黎"},{"pid":"f0c1d0d35aa1e5a4dc449755c6abd2a574ae9a75","tid":227053,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d3614a12b8b0e4810b77cdc6fa305047ea850e5","tid":227053,"uid":85929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"乜係香港讀會舒服啲咩？<br />\n淨係講讀書唔講環境 <br />\n要考試嘅科咪又係要背<br />\n大學你一個sem要讀完一科點同dse比<br />\n啲人話讀大學舒服可能係頭兩年齋玩唔讀<br />\n到最後兩年咪又係要死chur先畢到業（天才另計）"},{"pid":"2c1387f77fb3ae182251a1f8e1419fd190154739","tid":227053,"uid":6076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M0ES24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn